      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, having been garage-kept and frequently detailed; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use, the body remains straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean. The seating surfaces are supple with no cracks or tears, and the carpets have been protected by weather-resistant mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, premium sound system, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has followed a strict factory-recommended service schedule, with the most recent oil service and brake inspection completed just last month. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly, while the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. It currently sits on a set of tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-tier driving experience without the premium cost of a showroom-new model. Complete service records and both original key fobs are included.",
